{"tid":31664,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"香港想養柴犬既話係咪剩係得買呢一個方法?","createTime":"2016-12-09T19:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T07:22:26.000Z","uid":41662,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bacca8f7338d29e72209d64b4d83473ba30a9b4","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T19:12:37.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直都好想養 但又唔想買 好似助長左啲仆街咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打知有咩途徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願卑錢 但唔想比啲仆街當狗係生財工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be75c416f4e0fa904728917d3899ffa1116f05fd","tid":31664,"uid":13127,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T19:21:45.000Z","msg":"係pet shop買貓狗死全家 落地獄<br />\n留意下facebook好多領養page 見過都有柴犬<br />\n雖然柴犬真係好撚得意 但狗場真係地獄咁<br />\n千萬唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實唐狗都好可愛 考慮下"},{"pid":"92c5a3763018013a2d865cdbbb6a49c3752b6478","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T20:44:45.000Z","msg":"大把柴犬領養啦<br />\n不過通常係成犬比較多<br />\n想養柴犬要睇多d資料先好養<br />\n因為柴犬好難教所以成日先比人棄養<br />\n去Facebook一個叫Hong Kong Shiba Inu Rescue既群組<br />\n佢地專領養柴犬"},{"pid":"847236d15bb9e48bfaa92b2659633dd9e58b44a9","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:08:15.000Z","msg":"講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35a0ff9c84dd32054d1575bf694561b231936ef1","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係pet shop買貓狗死全家 落地獄<br />\n留意下facebook好多領養page 見過都有柴犬<br />\n雖然柴犬真係好撚得意 但狗場真係地獄咁<br />\n千萬唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實唐狗都好可愛 考慮下</blockquote><br />\n就係上facebook睇左幾個月都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我乜狗都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對狗好 好過對人好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過屋企麻麻地寵物 比較接愛到既係柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87330fc8c4f6cd06f9c2e8fbe62e20eb76584c6c","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把柴犬領養啦<br />\n不過通常係成犬比較多<br />\n想養柴犬要睇多d資料先好養<br />\n因為柴犬好難教所以成日先比人棄養<br />\n去Facebook一個叫Hong Kong Shiba Inu Rescue既群組<br />\n佢地專領養柴犬</blockquote><br />\n養成犬驚啲人細個教唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇過話柴犬好有性格<br />\n細個教唔好就捉蟲入屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af50b8e9d70f17fd6f6556d7f99494375ae513e8","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb21aaf7656cc0bd65d22ac68887e846464e2cd","tid":31664,"uid":59075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"有位巴打整左個領養apps,可睇下"},{"pid":"1f7b14544300f1853f00b70a9aeb2e25c8e80225","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有位巴打整左個領養apps,可睇下</blockquote><br />\n叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab9d826064347e417f1130fd1c44a851de01e0c","tid":31664,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有位巴打整左個領養apps,可睇下</blockquote><br />\n叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKAppDopt巴打嘅領養app<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2F7ev-fb.i&d=l0hbQcrkruqXjZccMqdCYgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=def57d57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i</a>"},{"pid":"6f704e47ae028c95c68b7706bd14c634bfe8d0d4","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大把柴犬領養啦<br />\n不過通常係成犬比較多<br />\n想養柴犬要睇多d資料先好養<br />\n因為柴犬好難教所以成日先比人棄養<br />\n去Facebook一個叫Hong Kong Shiba Inu Rescue既群組<br />\n佢地專領養柴犬</blockquote><br />\n養成犬驚啲人細個教唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇過話柴犬好有性格<br />\n細個教唔好就捉蟲入屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有d成犬都好乖因為曾經比人棄養過<br />\n想睇下夾唔夾先領養囉<br />\n仲有你叫細個教佢<br />\n有d人就係細個唔識教佢<br />\n就係搞到隻狗大個左收左行為問題<br />\n又咬人又吠人又護食"},{"pid":"93e81849b46032f2beae256f691f150c7b7a3ad2","tid":31664,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"唔好買，背後運作真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持領養代替購買<br />\n<br />\n唐狗都好好，易養，冇咁多病痛<br />\n<br />\n我都好鐘意柴犬，不過都知好難教，依家領養左隻唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf30b0f98aeb37293b7ff4424782c639dd26e2d","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢"},{"pid":"105cd13daf0b9ec011c02e59a51b50e1360de0d7","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大把柴犬領養啦<br />\n不過通常係成犬比較多<br />\n想養柴犬要睇多d資料先好養<br />\n因為柴犬好難教所以成日先比人棄養<br />\n去Facebook一個叫Hong Kong Shiba Inu Rescue既群組<br />\n佢地專領養柴犬</blockquote><br />\n養成犬驚啲人細個教唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇過話柴犬好有性格<br />\n細個教唔好就捉蟲入屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有d成犬都好乖因為曾經比人棄養過<br />\n睇下夾唔夾先領養囉<br />\n仲有你<span style=\"color: red;\">話</span>細個教佢<br />\n有d人就係細個唔識教佢<br />\n就係搞到隻狗大個左<span style=\"color: red;\">變</span>左行為問題<br />\n又咬人又吠人又護食</blockquote>"},{"pid":"87b9ee0c9a26a8565275d5247d43d83c42dc46d9","tid":31664,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"唔太支持買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會助長咗班仆街<br />\n佢哋見到有market就會係咁要狗媽媽生<br />\n狗媽媽子宮好快會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外 有啲petshop為咗啲狗狗睇落活躍啲 會幫佢哋打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十一二年前到唔興有領養 屋企人係petshop買隻八哥 返到黎先知好多病 又皮膚病又腸胃有事 唔夠一年就死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後養狗都係等人哋生咗唔要畀我哋或者領養<br />\n但因為嗰陣住公屋 愛協唔畀領養<br />\n屋企人好似搵另一嗰機構領養"},{"pid":"81c6139ff41ef7e4b704973224c2f805097a1aab","tid":31664,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:01:04.000Z","msg":"可以搵日本breeder買~"},{"pid":"16dc9241015002fb94d4ce890879470b1778a92f","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有位巴打整左個領養apps,可睇下</blockquote><br />\n叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKAppDopt巴打嘅領養app<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2F7ev-fb.i&d=l0hbQcrkruqXjZccMqdCYgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=def57d57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i</a></blockquote><br />\nan機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0879d09cfc2d9b3acfc4eaf7488ae74b523ea80a","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好買，背後運作真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持領養代替購買<br />\n<br />\n唐狗都好好，易養，冇咁多病痛<br />\n<br />\n我都好鐘意柴犬，不過都知好難教，依家領養左隻唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心 我令願唔養都唔會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見到啲救援片 睇見都覺心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6888678640e3004a0a02eb0d69eab3f7c10a67","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n巴打好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過套柴犬既戲 唔記得咩名<br />\n講過話你掉個波出去 隻柴唔會理尻你 要執自已執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec5262e2084b4348a49c7a63a259ea0c4308590","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大把柴犬領養啦<br />\n不過通常係成犬比較多<br />\n想養柴犬要睇多d資料先好養<br />\n因為柴犬好難教所以成日先比人棄養<br />\n去Facebook一個叫Hong Kong Shiba Inu Rescue既群組<br />\n佢地專領養柴犬</blockquote><br />\n養成犬驚啲人細個教唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇過話柴犬好有性格<br />\n細個教唔好就捉蟲入屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有d成犬都好乖因為曾經比人棄養過<br />\n睇下夾唔夾先領養囉<br />\n仲有你<span style=\"color: red;\">話</span>細個教佢<br />\n有d人就係細個唔識教佢<br />\n就係搞到隻狗大個左<span style=\"color: red;\">變</span>左行為問題<br />\n又咬人又吠人又護食</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n會呀 都會繼續搵領養<br />\n睇緣份啦 急唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會為養而養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1463a5e5517f597d4b939294d0a2fcf88871efe5","tid":31664,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n巴打好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過套柴犬既戲 唔記得咩名<br />\n講過話你掉個波出去 隻柴唔會理尻你 要執自已執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n秋田犬八千？李察基爾嗰套"},{"pid":"ac1ba3a2cf16a795bff57d5eed48e29bdaac2307","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔太支持買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會助長咗班仆街<br />\n佢哋見到有market就會係咁要狗媽媽生<br />\n狗媽媽子宮好快會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外 有啲petshop為咗啲狗狗睇落活躍啲 會幫佢哋打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十一二年前到唔興有領養 屋企人係petshop買隻八哥 返到黎先知好多病 又皮膚病又腸胃有事 唔夠一年就死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後養狗都係等人哋生咗唔要畀我哋或者領養<br />\n但因為嗰陣住公屋 愛協唔畀領養<br />\n屋企人好似搵另一嗰機構領養</blockquote><br />\n打針都聽過 好撚仆街<br />\n上網睇過話買完返屋企 又柯又嘔一星期後就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87603deecd8dbc3561582ab3b9b6b9578928f03d","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以搵日本breeder買~</blockquote><br />\n係咪繁殖場黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直有聽人推薦過 但買賣始終怕好繁殖場個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476228781db6fc8b664a9b606842814d96f6a72f","tid":31664,"uid":41662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n巴打好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過套柴犬既戲 唔記得咩名<br />\n講過話你掉個波出去 隻柴唔會理尻你 要執自已執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n秋田犬八千？李察基爾嗰套</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚好睇<br />\n記錯左原來個隻係秋田犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb2881df194bd2fff64bfe3fbc3dc0dc277435c","tid":31664,"uid":25463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"唔係果個品種既狗就一定果款性格<br />\n隻狗幾多歲之前發生過咩事都好<br />\n要教一定有得教<br />\n成犬可以簡一隻性情同你差唔多既<br />\n因為大左可以睇出佢屬於勇敢/細膽/cool/爛玩既狗<br />\n新手既話易d上手<br />\n文靜主人就咪簡活潑既<br />\n好out going既簡隻細膽只會你地一齊難受<br />\n要改變需要好多時間心機續樣改<br />\n領養唔係硬食就睇岩先啦"},{"pid":"d5f92ff99dc2d08df246f3583e55a29c98b774dc","tid":31664,"uid":20248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"柴犬好惡養<br />\n愈養愈洩氣<br />\n你要有心理準備<br />\n所以先有咁多狗場專收柴犬"},{"pid":"88dcd2c85477ee05216535a4d2f048fae5ec60fd","tid":31664,"uid":2431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"我有個friend前排買咗隻柴犬<br />\n我之前已經係咁勸佢領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本好多人都係為咗個潮流而揀動物品種唉"},{"pid":"7edaec3df42de86a72bd9a1cfc742b51ef3b3bbb","tid":31664,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:20:27.000Z","msg":"領養"},{"pid":"e3b30654c7be66f46ee614e1d5b53b8899d9bb6a","tid":31664,"uid":14442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有位巴打整左個領養apps,可睇下</blockquote><br />\n叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKAppDopt巴打嘅領養app<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2F7ev-fb.i&d=l0hbQcrkruqXjZccMqdCYgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=def57d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6568a134140c1951894eadd05289f9f8a133acf1","tid":31664,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"養唐狗好過，揾隻靚色d 同柴犬咪差唔多<br />\n又聽話 又少病痛"},{"pid":"7c180c892e525eedc8eaf35612302a717d64c1e0","tid":31664,"uid":43898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"一定要買既話就上網同日本或者台灣人買 價錢唔差幾多<br />\n香港d寵物店大多數都好仆街<br />\n如果唔要柴既就領養啦"},{"pid":"fff939547a8afc459bf69ff31e0800c8a1b8477c","tid":31664,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養唐狗好過，揾隻靚色d 同柴犬咪差唔多<br />\n又聽話 又少病痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見過唐狗毛色好靚真係柴犬咁<br />\n其實真係唔好養名種狗，佢地為左保持純種一定係近親相姦<br />\n一定有好多病痛"},{"pid":"764fd819052b311727e655a943b86590fb38741c","tid":31664,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n你sure 佢冇聾？"},{"pid":"f10580e3b45d6f4e516a84f494de907b02bf4c46","tid":31664,"uid":54901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係pet shop買貓狗死全家 落地獄<br />\n留意下facebook好多領養page 見過都有柴犬<br />\n雖然柴犬真係好撚得意 但狗場真係地獄咁<br />\n千萬唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實唐狗都好可愛 考慮下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ca2824a12f898dd2a6fe25ef20ad3a29bd0cc3","tid":31664,"uid":11950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"寵物店固然仆街<br />\n但見到無人買<br />\n比人困係個籠度真係好想救佢地出黎 好慘<br />\n向好個方面諗<br />\n如果無人買d狗就一世被困 配種 成世唔自由唔開心<br />\n領養係好d 買返黎都得 最重要係好好對佢<br />\n領養但棄養更加衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb0cb234ffc1943bb156527d9fa437d691ae7f4","tid":31664,"uid":3196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKAppDopt巴打嘅領養app<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappsto.re%2Fhk%2F7ev-fb.i&d=l0hbQcrkruqXjZccMqdCYgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=def57d57\" target=\"_blank\">https://appsto.re/hk/7ev-fb.i</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我個app好似冇柴犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff13b4694e63ba0d335f0bd80d76acba934086d","tid":31664,"uid":39514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物店固然仆街<br />\n但見到無人買<br />\n比人困係個籠度真係好想救佢地出黎 好慘<br />\n向好個方面諗<br />\n如果無人買d狗就一世被困 配種 成世唔自由唔開心<br />\n領養係好d 買返黎都得 最重要係好好對佢<br />\n領養但棄養更加衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你買完都係得個隻狗受益 到頭來變左另一隻狗代替佢位置受害"},{"pid":"52d7bd68836225d650a26590a87987d459f8dc70","tid":31664,"uid":39514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>寵物店固然仆街<br />\n但見到無人買<br />\n比人困係個籠度真係好想救佢地出黎 好慘<br />\n向好個方面諗<br />\n如果無人買d狗就一世被困 配種 成世唔自由唔開心<br />\n領養係好d 買返黎都得 最重要係好好對佢<br />\n領養但棄養更加衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你買完都係得個隻狗受益 到頭來變左另一隻狗代替佢位置受害</blockquote><br />\n然後到啲狗賣得七七八八 又迫啲狗繁殖無限loop<br />\n你個想法單方面可能係好 幫到一隻狗<br />\n不過其實係自欺欺人緊"},{"pid":"40354644fd4d498cd8e4dcc3ed47566a103dc86f","tid":31664,"uid":4468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n巴打好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過套柴犬既戲 唔記得咩名<br />\n講過話你掉個波出去 隻柴唔會理尻你 要執自已執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個隻勁鐘意玩波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴身到暈，你係屋行去邊佢跟到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d95d70cb90a994cdc9dac89f4f1228e46079d7","tid":31664,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"請支持唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唐狗個傻鳩樣其實好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fbbcc1797e932f2bcf465dc270d1533f19ce80","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n巴打好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過套柴犬既戲 唔記得咩名<br />\n講過話你掉個波出去 隻柴唔會理尻你 要執自已執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ne個真係好睇佢心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同佢玩拋波玩得最耐個次係半個鐘<br />\n最快個次係玩左來回兩次就唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85fe18204c81d599fcec07849c5fd48a8dfbe15","tid":31664,"uid":17294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:31:02.000Z","msg":"之前有隻6歲柴女喺荃灣等緊人領養，不過都成幾個月前，唔知仲喺唔喺度"},{"pid":"045adecd16d32ad5272b185b4df7e73a8a808e62","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講多少少先<br />\n其實寵物店有好多黑店<br />\nd寵物店唔只要佢老母狂生仔<br />\n柴犬一次只得3隻你諗下d狗B點黎喇<br />\n咪就係近親交配囉<br />\n搞到d狗B好多都有遺傳病<br />\n有d遺傳病係佢大大下先會出黎<br />\n所以到時d人買左以為冇事<br />\n點知大大下先知原來有咁既病後棄養<br />\n<br />\n利申：我就係上當年買中伏<br />\n間自稱專門店一樣都係黑店<br />\n買個陣明明係好靚但到佢5個月左右先病發<br />\n之後帶佢睇獸醫佢隻眼珠變到越來越大<br />\n大到合唔埋眼洗左好多錢係佢身上<br />\n後來獸醫話佢對眼已經壞死左變盲<br />\n但其實我覺得佢仲有一兩成視力<br />\n我同我屋企人都冇選擇棄養到佢<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解反而唔再帶佢睇獸醫<br />\n隻眼慢慢變返正常樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請支持領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ln5gx2pb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fln5gx2pb&h=2146f958&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病睇醫生 越睇越病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw巴打好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然佢對眼睇唔到野<br />\n但好彩佢都算乖又識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽街d柴友講佢地d柴犬唔識爹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有有其他狗吠佢佢又唔會吠返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過同一時間有6隻芝娃娃吠佢都冇反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇教過佢</blockquote><br />\n你sure 佢冇聾？</blockquote><br />\n冇聾到囉<br />\n佢識聽指令同知道有膠袋食物聲<br />\n玩拋波都係靠聽聲之後用臭覺<br />\n老豆打乞嚏佢會嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢都聾埋就真係幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7c8939a6b0c98f130ee3945b64ad19ae924774","tid":31664,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"其實唐狗都好得意 考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好買狗 領養d狗仔仲好 有d無人要好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b238574e84b2e4faf2527135ceac2150fb514129","tid":31664,"uid":10630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大把柴犬領養啦<br />\n不過通常係成犬比較多<br />\n想養柴犬要睇多d資料先好養<br />\n因為柴犬好難教所以成日先比人棄養<br />\n去Facebook一個叫Hong Kong Shiba Inu Rescue既群組<br />\n佢地專領養柴犬</blockquote><br />\n養成犬驚啲人細個教唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網睇過話柴犬好有性格<br />\n細個教唔好就捉蟲入屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有d成犬都好乖因為曾經比人棄養過<br />\n想睇下夾唔夾先領養囉<br />\n仲有你叫細個教佢<br />\n有d人就係細個唔識教佢<br />\n就係搞到隻狗大個左收左行為問題<br />\n又咬人又吠人又護食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好撚柒憎人遺棄動物<br />\n遺棄動物死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289f9ce6b959e73f991fcdd0203730981ac4eaad","tid":31664,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請支持唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唐狗個傻鳩樣其實好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前養過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以加老到自然死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好聽話 唔知係易教定佢天性係咁<br />\n不過屋企冇地方就難養啲 始終唐狗都大隻<br />\n同埋唐狗好似粗生粗養啲 冇咁多病痛"},{"pid":"2ecaa1e154f446c4f9700f8e1b400b7ca65806b3","tid":31664,"uid":11950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寵物店固然仆街<br />\n但見到無人買<br />\n比人困係個籠度真係好想救佢地出黎 好慘<br />\n向好個方面諗<br />\n如果無人買d狗就一世被困 配種 成世唔自由唔開心<br />\n領養係好d 買返黎都得 最重要係好好對佢<br />\n領養但棄養更加衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你買完都係得個隻狗受益 到頭來變左另一隻狗代替佢位置受害</blockquote><br />\n然後到啲狗賣得七七八八 又迫啲狗繁殖無限loop<br />\n你個想法單方面可能係好 幫到一隻狗<br />\n不過其實係自欺欺人緊</blockquote><br />\n唔打算養 不過覺得<br />\n領養&gt;買&gt;買/領養(棄養) <br />\n最怕領養完覺得自己好偉大 隻狗又免費 之後棄養"},{"pid":"f807c1cf6a7a35b3207a34daf27c8188acaa74b9","tid":31664,"uid":3196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請支持唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唐狗個傻鳩樣其實好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前養過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以加老到自然死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好聽話 唔知係易教定佢天性係咁<br />\n不過屋企冇地方就難養啲 始終唐狗都大隻<br />\n同埋唐狗好似粗生粗養啲 冇咁多病痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n確實係冇咁多病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51df8029b65091b12b38a02a13c176d6102e6797","tid":31664,"uid":46995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直都好想養 但又唔想買 好似助長左啲仆街咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打知有咩途徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願卑錢 但唔想比啲仆街當狗係生財工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千奇唔好買呀，雖然柴犬真係好難領養到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e627fa84d858827dbc438d4d6da2194f248590","tid":31664,"uid":12975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"屋企養緊唐狗表示得意到傻<br />\n又聽話又嗲人"},{"pid":"1c10d765ffdca62aab6ab4f76b248a143cfb4778","tid":31664,"uid":62866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"支持領養不棄養！"},{"pid":"dcfa9e56dd0a4e312dfc461a79e1fbe9e19f06e8","tid":31664,"uid":1970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"可以考慮下去Hong Kong doc rescue 領養呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d112dabeb072826e06d2d02e504896eaac0d7a1e","tid":31664,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企養緊唐狗表示得意到傻<br />\n又聽話又嗲人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好忠心 唔亂吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65849505c19dbea3d90af9bb8189bc196e9ca3c","tid":31664,"uid":5050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nn19SbY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnn19SbY.jpg&h=5099cbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衰妹真係妹有性格 似貓多過似狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba667267181c66bd4457