e2bc017cd7","tid":31664,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾多三千港紙 唔係就有得搵中介 之後自己網上揀日本當地既柴狗場 既柴？ 有規管好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必人人願意畀多啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4f948ffdb7651fe8489b17486993b3d5709f77","tid":31664,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"今日先有gp搵人領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我果隻係買架, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好後悔, 一諗到我隻柴既爸媽連名都無, <br />\n成世只係工具. 唔似我隻柴咁如珠如寶, <br />\n好後悔, 好心痛<br />\n勸各位支持領養, 唔好助長狗場"},{"pid":"76885e28eaa9249732532504317580c46cba32c4","tid":31664,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日先有gp搵人領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我果隻係買架, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好後悔, 一諗到我隻柴既爸媽連名都無, <br />\n成世只係工具. 唔似我隻柴咁如珠如寶, <br />\n好後悔, 好心痛<br />\n勸各位支持領養, 唔好助長狗場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger 唔係偽善 <br />\n但狗場啲狗媽媽好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被領養嘅動物唔代表佢哋有咩大問題/好曳<br />\n有時只係佢主人嘅問題 <br />\n乜嘢唔係由細養大 會難教其實都係藉口黎<br />\n你花多啲時間同佢相處就冇問題"},{"pid":"370f6fb08d1cda0fcc618de59b3105c72b4e8938","tid":31664,"uid":64354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"Ching如果想領養呀柴可以留意唔同寵物鋪 佢地有d年紀大左既柴犬賣唔出有機會放出離領養 我半年前先領養左隻三歲柴 大左係難教架喇 但睇住佢由唔理你到宜家跟住哂係好開心 所以慢慢搵下啦 養狗都講緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/013809_d96d1e77298cb796cdbbc0f5484e86b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F013809_d96d1e77298cb796cdbbc0f5484e86b4.jpg&h=6d95db9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch04q6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh04q6i.jpg&h=3b088d35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79bb5d5aa46fd416d582d9d5562d9d8add6006e8","tid":31664,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching如果想領養呀柴可以留意唔同寵物鋪 佢地有d年紀大左既柴犬賣唔出有機會放出離領養 我半年前先領養左隻三歲柴 大左係難教架喇 但睇住佢由唔理你到宜家跟住哂係好開心 所以慢慢搵下啦 養狗都講緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/013809_d96d1e77298cb796cdbbc0f5484e86b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F013809_d96d1e77298cb796cdbbc0f5484e86b4.jpg&h=6d95db9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch04q6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh04q6i.jpg&h=3b088d35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}